descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a new spell that is very overpowered. But for those of you who like over powered spells you may enjoy this. The spell itself has an unrelenting force effect that explodes with electricity and creating an instant kill. 
                                                    LOCATION:
You can find godsspell in the sleeping giant inn at riverwood on the bartenders coater search the counter and you will find it enjoy.
author: austin
